      • goTymeac

        private void goTymeac(java.lang.String input)
        Tymeac demonstration system go to Tymeac with a either a synchronous request or an asynchronous request, depending on the function. Initially, Tymeac Functions 1 - 4 are used as a syncRequest and Tymeac Functions 5 - 7 are used as an asyncRequest. Tymeac Function 8 is the recurrsive Function and is a syncRequest. You may wish to add code that checks for certain values and calls either a sync or async Tymeac method.
        Parameters:
        args - Object[]
